            "parameters": {
                "text": "=You are a professional scriptwriter specializing in cinematic historical documentaries.\n\nCreate a SHORT cinematic video script based on this historical event:\n{{ $json.description }} ({{ $json.year }})\n\nReturn ONLY a single clean paragraph (no markdown, no **bold**, no --- separators, no \"SCENE 1\" labels) that includes:\n- scene description\n- mood\n- camera movement\n- visual style\n\nMake it ready to be used directly as a Text-to-Video prompt. Keep it under 400 words.",
